I"]<ol>
  <li>Create <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/nginx/conf.d/map.conf</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>map $sent_http_content_type $expires {
  default                    off;
  ~(image|font|audio|video)/ max;
  ~application/              7d;
  ~text/                     7d;
  text/html                  off;
}

map $sent_http_content_type $logging {
  default 0;
  text/html 1;
}
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Include <code class="highlighter-rouge">map.conf</code> in <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/nginx/nginx.conf</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>http {
  ...

  include conf.d/map.conf;

  ...
}
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Add this lines to every site configuration:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>server {
  ...

  access_log /var/log/nginx/access.log combined if=$logging;

  add_header Cache-Control "public";
  expires $expires;
}
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

